relation: Targeted for the Atlys board, this project configures the two cameras on the VmodCAM for VGA resolution by using the built-in pixel binning and scaling features of the camera. The FPGA drives the HDMI out port with both video feeds. Works only with ISE Design Studio 12 and under.

Targeted for the Atlys board, this project configures the two cameras on the VmodCAM for maximum resolution (1600x1200) and frame rate (30fps). The two video feeds from both cameras are buffered in the DDR, while the FPGA drives the HDMI out port with either of the cameras. Works only with ISE Design Studio 12 and under.
